articles.title: We accomplished so much this week
articles.body: We managed to work together and build this app with so many hurdles, and still finished every day with a laugh and a smile. well done us!

articles.title: Testing is cool.
articles.body: Remembering how to test front end vs back end is hard but we did it. i think that is a huge accomplishment and i cant wait to continue using what we have learned about testing on the anonymates project.

articles.title: The anonymates Team
articles.body: The devs who work at anonymates seem to be really efficient, someone should try and give every single one of them a job!
